OL,3,CWorkers still being exploited 20 years
OL,4,Cafter Morecambe Bay disaster
OL,6,FWorkers are still being dangerously
OL,7,Fexploited in the UK 20 years on from
OL,8,Fthe disaster - which claimed the lives
OL,9,Fof 23 Chinese cocklepickers.
OL,11,FThe numbers of those trapped as modern
OL,12,Fslaves in the care sector has been
OL,13,Fincreasingly rising, as rules around
OL,14,Fimmigration were relaxed to help prop
OL,15,Fup the social care system.
