OL,3,CWorkers still being exploited 20 years
OL,4,Cafter Morecambe Bay disaster
OL,6,FThe move, by the Home Office in 2022,
OL,7,Fhoped to attract foreign workers into
OL,8,Fthe system, but organisations say the
OL,9,Fmove has led to some workers being
OL,10,F"duped" into paying excessive
OL,11,Fsponsorship fees and ending up
OL,12,Fbecoming trapped in a life of debt and
OL,13,Fexploitation.
OL,15,FMichael - not his real name - was one
OL,16,Fsuch worker. Enticed by the promise of
OL,17,Fa better quality of life, he left his
OL,18,Fhome in West Africa to settle in the
OL,19,FNorth West as a carer.
