OL,6,FThe agency in his home country
OL,7,Finitially told him it would cost #3000
OL,8,Ffor his sponsorship visa and agency
OL,9,Ffees - but after paying that amount he
OL,10,Fwas then told that he owed a further
OL,11,F#10,000, which would be deducted from
OL,12,Fhis weekly wage packet.
OL,14,FMichael says there were days he "went
OL,15,Fwithout eating or doing basic stuff",
OL,16,Fadding: "That's just the way it is.
OL,18,F"There's nothing you can do about it
OL,19,Fcause when you tell them they don't
OL,20,Fwant to listen.
