OL,6,F"Then you have just a few hours sleep
OL,7,Fand then you go back again at 4am the
OL,8,Fnext day and you keep going, just like
OL,9,Fthat."
OL,11,FMichael says there were times when the
OL,12,Fpressure became so overwhelming that
OL,13,Fhe broke down. When he told the
OL,14,Fagency, he claims that they responded
OL,15,Fby saying "there's no-one else to take
OL,16,Fyour place.
OL,18,F"If you don't do the work, whatever
OL,19,Fhappens to the clients is in your
OL,20,Fhands."
