OL,6,FThe Gangmasters and Labour Abuse
OL,7,FAuthority (GLAA), which was set up in
OL,8,Fthe wake of the Morecambe Bay tragedy,
OL,9,Fsays many are being charged almost 10
OL,10,Ftimes as much as they should be for
OL,11,Fvisas.
OL,13,FA total of 23 Chinese cockle pickers
OL,14,Fdrowned when they were cut off by the
OL,15,Ftide on 5 February 2004.
OL,17,FThe workers, all aged between 18 and
OL,18,F45, had been trafficked into the area
OL,19,Fby Liverpool gang-masters to work, and
OL,20,Fspoke little English and had no local
OL,21,Fknowledge or relevant skills
