OL,3,CWorkers still being exploited 20 years
OL,4,Cafter Morecambe Bay disaster
OL,6,FThe disaster led to the creation of
OL,7,Fthe GLAA, to try and better protect
OL,8,Fworkers - but it is now warning people
OL,9,Fare still being dangerously exploited.
OL,11,FSenior Investigating Officer Martin
OL,12,FPlimmer is one of those leading the
OL,13,Ffight against those "unscrupulous
OL,14,Fagents" who are "charging workers
OL,15,Fsometimes #10,000" for visas that
OL,16,Fwould cost "less than #1000" if they'd
OL,17,Fgone through legitimate means.
