OL,3,CWorkers still being exploited 20 years
OL,4,Cafter Morecambe Bay disaster
OL,6,FIn 2023, the anti-slavery charity
OL,7,FUnseen recorded at least 800 potential
OL,8,Fvictims of modern slavery within the
OL,9,Fsocial care sector alone, compared to
OL,10,Fthe 63 cases they recorded in 2021.
OL,12,FMartin Plimmer said: "excessive
OL,13,Fnumbers of people needed to be
OL,14,Frecruited into the industry, and the
OL,15,Fmajor part of that recruitment takes
OL,16,Fplaces in other countries where we
OL,17,Fcan't regulate that and can't oversee
OL,18,Fit.
