OL,4,Cafter Morecambe Bay disaster
OL,6,F"There's also a dire need for workers.
OL,7,FIf there aren't enough workers to fill
OL,8,Fthe vacancies, then the pressure is on
OL,9,Ffor people to work excessive hours and
OL,10,Fwork double shifts."
OL,12,FCauseway - the charity supporting
OL,13,FMichael - has also seen an increase in
OL,14,Fthe number of exploited carers walking
OL,15,Fthrough its doors.
