OL,6,FAmy Bond, the charity's chief
OL,7,Foperating officer, says some of those
OL,8,Fvictims have "received no pay at all"
OL,9,Fafter being forced to pay off their
OL,10,Fdebts "before receiving a penny of
OL,11,Ftheir own income."
OL,13,FOthers are forced to live in "really
OL,14,Fsqualid conditions or overcrowded
OL,15,Fhousing" and are forced to "scrape
OL,16,Faround for food", while living in fear
OL,17,Fof their exploiters.
