OL,6,FA Home Office spokesperson said:
OL,7,F"Modern slavery is a barbaric crime
OL,8,Fand we are committed to ensuring that
OL,9,Fthe necessary support is available to
OL,10,Fvictims of modern slavery to help them
OL,11,Frebuild their lives. We are bringing
OL,12,Fperpetrators of this heinous crime to
OL,13,Fjustice and are working with the
OL,14,Fpolice and operational partners to
OL,15,Fdrive up prosecutions."
